bert_similarity.py : downstream task (sentence-to-sentence similarity, sts) fine-tunning module
CPC_Class.py : CPC code object loading module
sampling.py : Positive / Negative sampling module
finetunnig.py : preprocessing & finetunning module
evaluating_similarity.py : calculate sts for testing set
evaluation_confusion_matrix.py : multi-label classification evaluating module


Dataset Google drive url : 

BERT_baseline.pt : fine-tunned model
df_claim_train_1M_pre_duplicates_removed_663.csv : train set rawdata
df_claim_test_1M_pre_duplicates_removed_663.csv : testing set rawdata
Structured_CPC.pickle : CPC code object
